<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: #1e293b;
      background: #fff;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    /* ───────────────── PORTADA ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .cover {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #fff;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 1050px;
      padding: 64px 60px 56px;
      page-break-after: always;
      position: relative;
    }

    .cover-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 420px;
      height: 420px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, .35) 0%, transparent 60%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .cover-glow2 {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -60px;
      left: -60px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139, 92, 246, .2) 0%, transparent 60%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .cover-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .cover-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(165, 180, 252, .4);
      color: #a5b4fc;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .cover-title {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .cover-sub {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .cover-url {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .07);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .12);
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
      margin-bottom: 72px;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .cover-score-row {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
      margin-bottom: 72px;
    }

    .cover-score-left {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      width: 200px;
    }

    .cover-score-right {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: middle;
      padding-left: 40px;
    }

    .big-score {
      width: 160px;
      height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 10px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .12);
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 28px;
    }

    .big-score-num {
      font-size: 58px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .big-score-num.green {
      color: #34d399;
    }

    .big-score-num.yellow {
      color: #fbbf24;
    }

    .big-score-num.red {
      color: #f87171;
    }

    .big-score-denom {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .4);
    }

    .big-score-word {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .5);
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cover-score-label {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .cover-score-desc {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .cover-footer-row {
      display: table;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .cover-footer-left {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: bottom;
    }

    .cover-footer-right {
      display: table-cell;
      vertical-align: bottom;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .cover-footer-left p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
    }

    .cover-footer-left strong {
      color: #94a3b8;
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cover-footer-right p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #475569;
    }

    .cover-footer-right strong {
      color: #a5b4fc;
      display: block;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ───────────────── PÁGINAS INTERNAS ─────────────────────────── */
    .page {
      padding: 48px 52px;
      page-break-after: auto;
    }

    .page-break {
      page-break-before: always;
    }

    .section-tag {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #6366f1;
      background: #eef2ff;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #0f172a;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1e293b;
    }

    p {
      color: #475569;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ───────────── CAJA RESUMEN ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .summary-box {
      background: #f8fafc;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
      border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
      padding: 22px 26px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #334155;
    }

    /* ───────────── CONTADORES ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .counts-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: separate;
      border-spacing: 8px 0;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .count-box {
      padding: 16px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .count-box.c-crit {
      background: #fef2f2;
    }

    .count-box.c-high {
      background: #fff7ed;
    }

    .count-box.c-med {
      background: #fffbeb;
    }

    .count-box.c-low {
      background: #eff6ff;
    }

    .count-n {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .count-box.c-crit .count-n {
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .count-box.c-high .count-n {
      color: #ea580c;
    }

    .count-box.c-med .count-n {
      color: #d97706;
    }

    .count-box.c-low .count-n {
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    .count-l {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    /* ───────────── CAJA URGENTE ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .urgent-box {
      background: #fff5f5;
      border: 1px solid #fecaca;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .urgent-title {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #991b1b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .urgent-row {
      padding: 5px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fee2e2;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7f1d1d;
    }

    .urgent-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    /* ───────────── GRID PUNTUACIONES ─────────────────────────────── */
    .scores-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: separate;
      border-spacing: 10px 0;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .score-box {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 18px 12px;
      text-align: center;
      vertical-align: top;
      width: 25%;
    }

    .score-area {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .score-val {
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .score-box.green .score-val {
      color: #059669;
    }

    .score-box.yellow .score-val {
      color: #d97706;
    }

    .score-box.red .score-val {
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .score-qual {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .score-box.green .score-qual {
      color: #059669;
    }

    .score-box.yellow .score-qual {
      color: #d97706;
    }

    .score-box.red .score-qual {
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    /* ───────────── NARRATIVA ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .narrative-box {
      background: #fafafa;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 22px 26px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #334155;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }

    /* ───────────── HALLAZGOS ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    .finding {
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      page-break-inside: avoid;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .finding.critical {
      border-left: 5px solid #dc2626;
    }

    .finding.high {
      border-left: 5px solid #ea580c;
    }

    .finding.medium {
      border-left: 5px solid #d97706;
    }

    .finding.low {
      border-left: 5px solid #2563eb;
    }

    .finding-head {
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }

    .fh-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .fh-badge-cell {
      width: 74px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      padding-right: 14px;
    }

    .fh-title-cell {
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .badge.critical {
      background: #fef2f2;
      color: #dc2626;
    }

    .badge.high {
      background: #fff7ed;
      color: #ea580c;
    }

    .badge.medium {
      background: #fffbeb;
      color: #d97706;
    }

    .badge.low {
      background: #eff6ff;
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    .f-title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .f-code {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .finding-body {
      padding: 14px 20px;
    }

    .impact-tag {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #7c3aed;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .impact-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #475569;
    }

    /* ───────────── PIE DE PÁGINA ─────────────────────────────────── */
    .page-footer {
      margin-top: 36px;
      padding-top: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .pf-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .pf-left {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .pf-right {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      vertical-align: middle;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .pf-left strong {
      color: #6366f1;
    }

    /* ───────────── PÁGINA CTA ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .cta-page {
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #fff;
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 1050px;
      padding: 72px 60px;
      page-break-before: always;
      position: relative;
    }

    .cta-glow {
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 460px;
      height: 460px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(99, 102, 241, .28) 0%, transparent 60%);
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .cta-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-width: 540px;
    }

    .cta-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(165, 180, 252, .4);
      color: #a5b4fc;
      padding: 4px 14px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .cta-h1 {
      font-size: 34px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cta-h1 span {
      color: #a5b4fc;
    }

    .cta-body {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .cta-items {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .cta-item {
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .07);
    }

    .cta-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .cti-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .cti-check {
      width: 22px;
      vertical-align: top;
      color: #34d399;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .cti-text {
      vertical-align: top;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .cta-contact {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .cta-contact-line {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .cta-contact-line strong {
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .cta-hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .1);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .author-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .author-av-cell {
      width: 56px;
      vertical-align: middle;
      padding-right: 16px;
    }

    .author-av {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #8b5cf6);
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .author-info-cell {
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .author-name {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .author-role {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ PORTADA ══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="cover">
    <div class="cover-glow"></div>
    <div class="cover-glow2"></div>
    <div class="cover-inner">

      <div class="cover-tag">AuditaWeb &middot; Informe Profesional</div>
      <div class="cover-title">Auditor&iacute;a Web<br>Completa</div>
      <div class="cover-sub">An&aacute;lisis t&eacute;cnico y de negocio con plan de acci&oacute;n</div>
      <div class="cover-url">{{url}}</div>

      <div class="cover-score-row">
        <div class="cover-score-left">
          <div class="big-score">
            <div class="big-score-num {{colorClass globalScore}}">{{globalScore}}</div>
            <div class="big-score-denom">/100</div>
            <div class="big-score-word">{{scoreLabel globalScore}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cover-score-right">
          <div class="cover-score-label">Puntuaci&oacute;n global</div>
          <div class="cover-score-desc">
            {{#if (gt globalScore 79)}}Tu web est&aacute; en buena forma{{else}}{{#if (gt globalScore 59)}}Hay margen de
            mejora importante{{else}}Problemas que cuestan clientes{{/if}}{{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cover-footer-row">
        <div class="cover-footer-left">
          <p><strong>Fecha de an&aacute;lisis</strong>{{date}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cover-footer-right">
          <p><strong>Ra&uacute;l Huete</strong>Desarrollador web &middot; zero2dev.es</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ RESUMEN EJECUTIVO ════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="page">
    <div class="section-tag">01 &mdash; Resumen Ejecutivo</div>
    <h2>Situaci&oacute;n actual de tu web</h2>

    <div class="summary-box">
      Este informe recoge el an&aacute;lisis completo de <b>{{url}}</b> realizado el {{date}}.
      Se han evaluado cuatro &aacute;reas cr&iacute;ticas: <b>velocidad de carga, posicionamiento en Google,
        seguridad</b> y <b>accesibilidad</b>.
      La puntuaci&oacute;n global es <b>{{globalScore}}/100</b> &mdash;
      {{#if (gt globalScore 79)}}tu web est&aacute; en buena forma aunque siempre hay margen de mejora.{{else}}{{#if (gt
      globalScore 59)}}hay problemas que pueden estar fren&aacute;ndote en Google y reduciendo tus
      conversiones.{{else}}existen problemas serios que probablemente te est&aacute;n costando clientes ahora
      mismo.{{/if}}{{/if}}
    </div>

    <table class="counts-table">
      <tr>
        <td class="count-box c-crit">
          <div class="count-n">{{criticalCount}}</div>
          <div class="count-l">Cr&iacute;ticos</div>
        </td>
        <td class="count-box c-high">
          <div class="count-n">{{highCount}}</div>
          <div class="count-l">Altos</div>
        </td>
        <td class="count-box c-med">
          <div class="count-n">{{mediumCount}}</div>
          <div class="count-l">Medios</div>
        </td>
        <td class="count-box c-low">
          <div class="count-n">{{lowCount}}</div>
          <div class="count-l">Bajos</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    {{#if urgentFindings.length}}
    <div class="urgent-box">
      <div class="urgent-title">Problemas que requieren atenci&oacute;n inmediata</div>
      {{#each urgentFindings}}
      <div class="urgent-row">&#9658; {{#if this.title}}{{this.title}}{{else}}{{this.code}}{{/if}}</div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <h2 style="margin-top:24px;">Puntuaciones por &aacute;rea</h2>
    <table class="scores-table">
      <tr>
        {{#each scores}}
        <td class="score-box {{colorClass this}}">
          <div class="score-area">{{scoreAreaName @key}}</div>
          <div class="score-val">{{this}}</div>
          <div class="score-qual">{{scoreLabel this}}</div>
        </td>
        {{/each}}
      </tr>
    </table>

    {{#if narrative}}
    <div class="section-tag" style="margin-top:4px;">An&aacute;lisis de impacto</div>
    <h2>Qu&eacute; significa esto para tu negocio</h2>
    <div class="narrative-box">{{stripMd narrative}}</div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="page-footer">
      <table class="pf-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="pf-left"><strong>AuditaWeb</strong> &middot; Informe confidencial</td>
          <td class="pf-right">{{url}} &middot; {{date}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════ HALLAZGOS ════════════════════════════════ -->
  {{#if findings.length}}
  <div class="page page-break">
    <div class="section-tag">02 &mdash; Hallazgos Detallados</div>
    <h2>{{totalFindings}} problemas detectados</h2>

    <p style="margin-bottom:22px; font-size:13px;">
      Ordenados de mayor a menor urgencia. Para cada problema se explica el impacto real en tu negocio.
    </p>

    {{#each findings}}
    <div class="finding {{this.severity}}">
      <div class="finding-head">
        <table class="fh-table">
          <tr>
            <td class="fh-badge-cell">
              <span class="badge {{this.severity}}">{{severityLabel this.severity}}</span>
            </td>
            <td class="fh-title-cell">
              <div class="f-title">{{#if this.title}}{{this.title}}{{else}}{{this.code}}{{/if}}</div>
              <div class="f-code">{{this.code}}</div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      {{#if this.businessImpact}}
      <div class="finding-body">
        <div class="impact-tag">POR QUE IMPORTA</div>
        <div class="impact-text">{{this.businessImpact}}</div>
      </div>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    {{/each}}

    <div class="page-footer">
      <table class="pf-table">
        <tr>
          <td class="pf-left"><strong>AuditaWeb</strong> &middot; Hallazgos detallados</td>
          <td class="pf-right">{{url}} &middot; {{date}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  {{/if}}

  <!-- ═══════════════════ CTA ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="cta-page">
    <div class="cta-glow"></div>
    <div class="cta-inner">

      <div class="cta-tag">03 &mdash; Siguiente Paso</div>
      <div class="cta-h1">&iquest;Quieres que resuelva<br><span>todo esto por ti?</span></div>
      <div class="cta-body">
        Ya sabes qu&eacute; falla y por qu&eacute; te est&aacute; costando dinero.
        Yo me encargo de solucionarlo todo &mdash; sin que tengas que entender una sola l&iacute;nea de c&oacute;digo.
      </div>

      <div class="cta-items">
        <div class="cta-item">
          <table class="cti-table">
            <tr>
              <td class="cti-check">&#10003;</td>
              <td class="cti-text">Corrijo todos los problemas identificados en este informe</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-item">
          <table class="cti-table">
            <tr>
              <td class="cti-check">&#10003;</td>
              <td class="cti-text">Tu web cargando r&aacute;pido en m&oacute;vil y ordenador</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-item">
          <table class="cti-table">
            <tr>
              <td class="cti-check">&#10003;</td>
              <td class="cti-text">SEO t&eacute;cnico correcto para que Google te encuentre y te posicione</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-item">
          <table class="cti-table">
            <tr>
              <td class="cti-check">&#10003;</td>
              <td class="cti-text">Seguridad reforzada: tus datos y los de tus clientes protegidos</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
